# Agent workflow

When implementing:
1. Read relevant files first.
2. Propose the smallest change set that satisfies the request.
3. Edit existing files before creating new ones.
4. Keep functions short and named clearly.
5. Add TODO comments only when necessary.
6. Do not introduce libraries without asking.

When uncertain:
- Ask for clarification instead of inventing a subsystem.
- Use project docs in .cursor/docs and external @Docs references.